dct_title_s: Die insul Madagascar : heisset sonsten auch Dauphine, oder die S. Laurenzen-insul
dct_description_sm: Scale approximately 1:40,000,000 ; Relief shown pictorially ; At top: 'XVI.b' ; Map displays navigation hazards ; Covers Madagascar, Mozambique coast, and neighboring islands ; Ulm : Publisher not identified
